title: Distrust v1.0.3
description: Inspired by John Carpenter's The Thing.A helicopter crash left a group of explorers stranded near an Arctic base. As they try to find a way back, all they are doing is sinking deeper into a nightmare scenario. When they sleep, they attract a terrifying force that sucks the life out of their bodies, but the longer they battle exhaustion and stay awake, the less likely they are to survive...As the survivors try to sleep just enough to stave off fatigue without dying, they slowly go mad and
